data.description: Check out this great lake home! There are 3 Bedrooms, 2 full baths and plenty of additional living and relaxing space inside and out. On the main level, you'll find a spacious great room with vaulted ceilings open to the kitchen and providing access to the deck with awesome views of Riley Lake. There are two bedrooms on the main, one with an ensuite bath and a great view with deck access. The walkout basement features three large versatile rooms, one of which is being used as a bedroom, and two with sliding doors going out to the lake, providing great views. The back yard provides plenty of space for gathering, playing, relaxing around the fire pit or fishing while enjoying the peaceful well stocked lake. An HSA Home Warranty is included.
